Manga
A manga adaptation illustrated by Yutaka Ohhori began serialization in Square Enix's  manga magazine Monthly Big Gangan on September 25, 2018. The manga's chapters have been collected into thirteen  volumes as of September 2025. The manga is published digitally in North America by Comikey and by Square Enix via their Manga UP! Global app.
